quran[10{c,v,t}:
38,84,"farmaya"" to haq yeh hai, aur mein haq hi kaha karta hon"
38,85,"ke mein jahannum ko tujh se aur unn sab logon se bhar dun ga jo inn insanon mein se teri pairwi karen ge """
38,86,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) inn se keh do ke mein is tableegh par tum se koi ajar nahi maangta, aur nah mein banawati logon mein se hon"
38,87,yeh to aik nasiyaat hai tamam Jahan walon ke liye
38,88,aur thori muddat hi guzray gi ke tumhe is ka haal khud maloom ho jaye ga
39,1,iss kitaab ka nuzool Allah zabardast aur Dana ki taraf se hai
39,2,"( aeMuhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam) yeh kitaab hum ne tumhari taraf brhq nazil ki hai, lehaza tum Allah hi ki bandagi karo deen ko usi ke liye khalis karte hue"
39,3,"khabardaar, deen khalis Allah ka haq hai rahay woh log jinhon ne uss ke siwa dosray sarparast bana rakhay hain ( aur apne iss feal ki tojeeh yeh karte hain ke ) hum to unn ki ibadat sirf is liye karte hain ke woh Allah taq hamari rasai kara den, Allah yaqeenan unn ke darmain unn tamam baton ka faisla kar day ga jin mein woh ikhtilaaf kar rahay hain Allah kisi aisay shakhs ko hadaayat nahi deta jo jhoota aur munkir haq ho"
39,4,"agar Allah kisi ko beta banana chahta to apni makhlooq mein se jis ko chahta bargzida kar laita, pak hai woh is se ( ke koi uss ka beta ho ), woh Allah hai akela aur sab par ghalib"
39,5,"is ne asmano aur zameen ko brhq peda kya hai wohi din par raat aur raat par din ko liptahai usi ne Sooraj aur chaand ko is terhan maskhar kar rakha hai ke har aik aik waqt muqarrar taq chalay ja raha hai jaan rakho, woh zabardast hai aur dar guzar karne wala hai"
